{"type":"text","timestamp":1775899731069,"sessionID":"ses_28424d447ffePQtL9U3b1uD4b3","part":{"id":"prt_d7bdf3ecb001BCGI5gJSKlkv1C","messageID":"msg_d7bdf360d001Q2sZ2YbJFintlk","sessionID":"ses_28424d447ffePQtL9U3b1uD4b3","type":"text","text":"The `delta-spec.md` file has been created successfully at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-026/delta-spec.md`.\n\n## Summary\n\nThe specification includes **18 major requirements** with **70+ GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios** covering:\n\n### KubernetesProvider Requirements:\n- **Initialization and Configuration** - Default/custom namespace, kubeconfig, verbose mode\n- **Namespace Management** - Ensure namespace exists, handle creation failures\n- **Name Sanitization** - Lowercase conversion, invalid character replacement, truncation\n- **Agent Deployment** - Full deployment flow with entrypoint, replicas, NodePort, env vars\n- **Deployment/Service Resource Creation** - Proper Kubernetes resource generation\n- **Readiness Waiting** - Timeout handling, status polling\n- **Status Retrieval** - Running/not_found/scaling states\n- **Agent Deletion** - Idempotent deletion with 404 handling\n\n### AgentCubeProvider Requirements:\n- **Initialization** - Default/custom namespace configuration\n- **AgentRuntime CR Deployment** - Full CR creation with readiness probes, URL injection, timeout settings, image pull secrets\n- **AgentRuntime CR Retrieval** - Get by name/namespace with API group/version compliance\n\n### Integration Requirements:\n- **PublishRuntime** - Provider selection, prerequisite validation\n- **StatusRuntime** - Status interpretation for both providers\n- **InvokeRuntime** - Endpoint construction for AgentRuntime CR\n\n### Error Handling:\n- Kubernetes API errors (connection, permissions, conflicts)\n- Input validation (NodePort range, port numbers, empty values)\n\nThe file also includes:\n- **Data Model Reference** with complete class signatures\n- **File Index** for target implementation files\n- **Dependencies** table (kubernetes, pydantic, PyYAML)\n- **Integration Points** showing how providers connect to Runtime classes\n- **Implementation Notes** with 10 key implementation guidelines","time":{"start":1775899731066,"end":1775899731066}}}
